                    <span>A REAL story told REALLY well. <BR>I listened to it on tape. One of my top five favorite books of all time. I would not have found it if my librarian hadn't suggested it. Couldn't put it down - If you are a man (or woman) in search of true adventure from days gone by then this is the book for you. This insanely difficult journey reveals the true character and spirit of these men in their effort just to stay alive. It feels like you are almost there with them, but glad that you aren't. <BR>A true vision quest. <BR>Buy it- <BR>Read it - <BR>Then give it to a friend - It's that GOOD!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">First-rate</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
